resources.string: When there is a data connection available
When software errors occur on a device, sending a diagnostic report may result in a data usage charge, and it is recommended that you apply for a data package from your carrier.
Please assist us in improving product and service, and permit us to collect diagnostic data when you incur software error or crashes. You can modify this option in setting later.
You are about to leave our user experience program. Software errors that occur on your mobile phone will not be retained and sent, so this may not improve your experience of using the mobile phone!
